                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Partenaire IHE International</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Integrating the Healthcare Enterprise - Standards d'interopérabilité</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Chef de file "Digitalisation"</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Transform Health Sénégal avec Enda Santé</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Membre de la Commission nationale</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Gouvernance des données de santé au Sénégal</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-amber-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">West & Central Africa Network</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Avec Africa CDC, Digital Square et partenaires</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Notre Parcours - Timeline -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="inline-block bg-senegal-green/10 text-senegal-green text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4">
          Notre Histoire
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          5 ans de développement au Sénégal
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Un parcours jalonné de partenariats stratégiques et de reconnaissances internationales.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Timeline line -->
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 h-full w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-sante-500 via-senegal-yellow to-senegal-green hidden lg:block"></div>

        <!-- 2025 -->
        <div class="relative mb-12">
          <div class="lg:flex items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-12 lg:text-right mb-6 lg:mb-0">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border-l-4 border-sante-500 lg:border-l-0 lg:border-r-4">
                <span class="inline-block bg-sante-500 text-white text-sm font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-3">2025</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Expansion des partenariats institutionnels</h3>
                <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2 lg:flex-row-reverse lg:text-right">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sante-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Rencontres avec l'ANSD, Sécurité sociale, CMU</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2 lg:flex-row-reverse lg:text-right">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sante-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
