                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2 lg:flex-row-reverse lg:text-right">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sante-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Pilote Centre de santé Philippe Senghor</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2 lg:flex-row-reverse lg:text-right">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sante-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Collaboration Département Partenariat Ministère Santé</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden lg:flex w-12 h-12 bg-sante-500 rounded-full items-center justify-center z-10 mx-auto shadow-lg">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">25</span>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-12"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2024 -->
        <div class="relative mb-12">
          <div class="lg:flex items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-12"></div>
            <div class="hidden lg:flex w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500 rounded-full items-center justify-center z-10 mx-auto shadow-lg">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">24</span>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-12 mb-6 lg:mb-0">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500">
                <span class="inline-block bg-blue-500 text-white text-sm font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-3">2024</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Reconnaissance internationale & Tests pilotes</h3>
                <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Connectathon IHE Europe</strong> - Italie (Juin)</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Tests pilotes IME Dakar + établissements scolaires</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Partenariat DCMS & Inspection Académique</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Tests Centre de santé Philippe Senghor & UCAD</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2023 -->
        <div class="relative mb-12">
          <div class="lg:flex items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-12 lg:text-right mb-6 lg:mb-0">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border-l-4 border-purple-500 lg:border-l-0 lg:border-r-4">
                <span class="inline-block bg-purple-500 text-white text-sm font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-3">2023</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Rayonnement africain & Standardisation</h3>
                <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-2">
